<body style="background-color:#563d7c">

<div class="container">  
  <div class="center-block" style="width:200px;margin-top:30px;">
    <a href="https://fbmocktest.herokuapp.com/">
      <img src="https://s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/fbmock/mocktestprofile.png" width="200" height="200"/>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <div class="panel">
      <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
        <li id="mocktesttab" class="active" style="cursor:pointer"><a>MockTest</a></li>
        <li id="paymenttab"  style="cursor:pointer"  ><a>Payment</a></li>   
      </ul>
      <div id="main_panel">
        <div style="padding: 10px; height: 300px;">
          <p>Welcome to Mock Test chatbot.
          Mock test is a facebook chatbot which helps students preparing for competitive exams like CAT, GRE, GMAT, 
          SNAP, XAT etc etc to sharpen there aptitude.</p> 
          <p>Mock test chatbot conducts mini mock tests on facebook chat or on facebook messenger. Each mock test contains 
          10 questions and it needs to be solved in 15mins. Each test costs just rupees 5. The tests can be taken from 
          anywhere anytime at the users convinience. The first two tests are provided free of charge. A student also gets a 
          free test on scoring full marks in a test.</p>
          <p>Press the Start Test button to take your first test.</p>

        </div>
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block" style="width:300px; margin: 20px auto 0px auto;" href="https://m.me/mocktestchatbot">Start Test</a>
        
      </div>
      <div id="payment_panel" style="display:none;">
        <h3 class="text-center">Login for Payment</h3>
        <form action="/payments/login" method="post" role="form">
            
            <div class="form-group"> 

                <input style="margin-bottom:10px;" autofocus="true" class="form-control" id="userid" name="userid" placeholder="userid" tabindex="1">

                <input autofocus="false" class="form-control" id="password" name="password" placeholder="password" tabindex="1" type="password">
            </div>
            
            <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block" name="commit" tabindex="3" type="submit" value="Log In">Submit</button>
        </form>
        <p style="color:#79589f; font-size:12px; font-style: italic; margin:30px; "> * userid and dynamic password is provided in the add money section inside chatbot.</p>
      </div>  
    </div>
  </div>

</div> 

